WEBVTT

29eee94e-da18-4017-96e4-6a8eb876ef12-0
00:00:00.520 --> 00:00:03.526
To be able to easily communicate
with the people you message and

29eee94e-da18-4017-96e4-6a8eb876ef12-1
00:00:03.526 --> 00:00:06.023
call the most through Kye,
you'll need to add them as

29eee94e-da18-4017-96e4-6a8eb876ef12-2
00:00:06.023 --> 00:00:06.440
contacts.

7e1ebc0d-f9bc-4a6c-ac68-0a9e9192f80e-0
00:00:07.200 --> 00:00:09.948
By adding someone as a contact,
you can quickly see whether

7e1ebc0d-f9bc-4a6c-ac68-0a9e9192f80e-1
00:00:09.948 --> 00:00:12.742
they're currently online and if
so you can get in touch with

7e1ebc0d-f9bc-4a6c-ac68-0a9e9192f80e-2
00:00:12.742 --> 00:00:15.399
them through text messages or
calls with just a couple of

7e1ebc0d-f9bc-4a6c-ac68-0a9e9192f80e-3
00:00:15.399 --> 00:00:15.720
clicks.

067333e6-68c1-4ddf-b066-d2458483dfea-0
00:00:16.520 --> 00:00:19.305
To add a contact, click in the
search bar and start typing the

067333e6-68c1-4ddf-b066-d2458483dfea-1
00:00:19.305 --> 00:00:19.880
erson's name.

339a8bd7-2ed2-47d0-8678-15b25c4fa75a-0
00:00:21.440 --> 00:00:23.920
If they have a Kye account, they
should show U in the list of

339a8bd7-2ed2-47d0-8678-15b25c4fa75a-1
00:00:23.920 --> 00:00:25.320
results here in the Kye
directory.

321f1a8a-5bd5-493e-8a7f-94930fe415ca-0
00:00:26.120 --> 00:00:28.645
Once you've located them, you
can right click their name and

321f1a8a-5bd5-493e-8a7f-94930fe415ca-1
00:00:28.645 --> 00:00:29.970
choose to add them as a contact.

7b264f6b-eaf2-4c89-b6fc-dd180e542f7a-0
00:00:31.330 --> 00:00:33.850
Now if I clear the search, you
can see with Contacts selected,

7b264f6b-eaf2-4c89-b6fc-dd180e542f7a-1
00:00:33.850 --> 00:00:35.370
Oliver has been added to my
contacts.

e0b4c434-12c8-49ad-91bd-c498d89633b5-0
00:00:36.050 --> 00:00:38.561
Now you can also search for
people by their usernames, which

e0b4c434-12c8-49ad-91bd-c498d89633b5-1
00:00:38.561 --> 00:00:40.825
can be useful if the person
you're searching for has a

e0b4c434-12c8-49ad-91bd-c498d89633b5-2
00:00:40.825 --> 00:00:43.377
common name, in which case you
might see multile results when

e0b4c434-12c8-49ad-91bd-c498d89633b5-3
00:00:43.377 --> 00:00:44.530
you search for them by name.

f08c01fc-5188-4072-81a6-50ee1af244de-0
00:00:45.090 --> 00:00:47.514
In those cases you might want to
ask your friend or colleague

f08c01fc-5188-4072-81a6-50ee1af244de-1
00:00:47.514 --> 00:00:48.570
what their Kye username is.

a91c3a8d-0852-4f7f-8ac7-959b52185da2-0
00:00:48.890 --> 00:00:53.134
Then you can just type that
username into the search field

a91c3a8d-0852-4f7f-8ac7-959b52185da2-1
00:00:53.134 --> 00:00:57.450
and then you can add them as a
contact when they show UO O.

ef9dadc6-bed9-4166-b130-6627e693c1e9-0
00:00:57.450 --> 00:00:59.410
That's how to add contacts to
your Kye account.